            "initialPosition": "mfa-scenario2__tooltip3 scenario-tooltip--anchor",
            "style": "scenario--tooltip__pin glyph--pin text--white glyphicon glyphicon-pushpin",
            "position": "top-right",
            "type": "problem"
          },
          {
            "htmlId": "scenario2_tooltip4",
            "personStatement": "When I go overseas for work, I worry about losing access to my work should I lose my smart card and IT is unavailable",
            "businessStatement": "Implementing biometric based two factor validation on work computers are often complex, more expensive and may involve being tied down to one hardware vendor's solution.",
            "initialPosition": "mfa-scenario2__tooltip4 scenario-tooltip--anchor",
            "style": "scenario--tooltip__pin glyph--pin text--white glyphicon glyphicon-pushpin",
            "position": "top-right",
            "type": "problem"
          },
          {
            "htmlId": "scenario2_tooltip5",
            "businessStatement": "I can just use a PIN when signing on to my work computer, so I don't lose productivity when I forget my smart card.",
            "initialPosition": "mfa-scenario2__tooltip5 scenario-tooltip--anchor",
            "style": "scenario--tooltip__pin glyph--pin text--white glyphicon glyphicon-pushpin",
            "position": "top-right",
            "type": "solution_start"
          },
          {
            "htmlId": "scenario2_tooltip6",
            "businessStatement": "Entering a PIN may not be required if I have a new computer that can recognize my face or fingerprint, providing quicker access to work resources.",
            "initialPosition": "mfa-scenario2__tooltip6 scenario-tooltip--anchor",
            "style": "scenario--tooltip__pin glyph--pin text--white glyphicon glyphicon-pushpin",
            "position": "top-right",
            "type": "solution"
          },
          {
            "htmlId": "scenario2_tooltip7",
            "businessStatement": "This form of authentication makes it more difficult for attackers to access my work information by requiring them to have both my work computer and my PIN/fingerprint.",
            "initialPosition": "mfa-scenario2__tooltip7 scenario-tooltip--anchor",
            "style": "scenario--tooltip__pin glyph--pin text--white glyphicon glyphicon-pushpin",
            "position": "bottom-left",
            "type": "solution"
          },
